title: edge of the empire.pdf
description:
Star wars: Edge of the empire the roleplaying game. The full game, not the beta book.
Sorry, the quality ain't perfect but my scanner had better days.

Anyways, didn't find the book anywhere so I put it up myself, but you really should buy the book if you want to GM. For players on the other hand it is nice with a .pdf, we all know that some people hog the rulebook and that an IPAD each is great when you make characters or so.

Nice game, I was critical about the dice first but I came around. :)
